# Serein AI — Intelligent Chatbot Training & Multi-Model NLP Pipeline

## Goal

Transform the current Serein AI chatbot from a simple keyword-based sentiment + GPT-4o relay into a **seriously trained, multi-model NLP system** that:
1. **Answers every question positively** — never returns a single generic fallback
2. Uses **real sentiment analysis models** (VADER, TextBlob, custom AFINN ensemble)
3. Is **trained on real datasets** from Kaggle & IEEE (EmpatheticDialogues, GoEmotions, Counsel Chat, Mental Health FAQ)
4. Has a **massive local knowledge base** so it can answer without API calls when possible
5. Uses **Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)** — searches the knowledge base first, then uses GPT-4o with context for comprehensive answers

---

