## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Python Backend Required**: This plan adds a Python FastAPI server alongside your frontend. The backend handles all ML/NLP processing. The frontend will call the backend API instead of calling OpenAI directly.

> [!WARNING]
> **OpenAI API Key**: Your API key is currently hardcoded in `app.js` (exposed to the browser). Moving it to the Python backend is a security improvement — the key will only exist server-side.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Dataset Downloads**: We will programmatically download and process datasets from Kaggle/HuggingFace. No manual downloads needed. The processed data will be stored as JSON knowledge bases (~5-10MB total).

