## Response Quality Guarantee

The multi-tier fallback chain ensures **EVERY question gets a meaningful answer**:

```
Tier 1: Knowledge Base Match (similarity > 0.6)
  → Uses real counseling/empathy data, paraphrased
  
Tier 2: RAG + GPT-4o (similarity 0.3-0.6)
  → GPT-4o with relevant KB examples as context
  
Tier 3: Pure GPT-4o (no KB match)
  → Enriched system prompt with detected emotion + intent
  
Tier 4: Trained Templates (API failure)
  → 500+ curated templates matched by emotion + topic + intensity
  
Tier 5: Dynamic Composition (all else fails)
  → Assembles response from empathy + understanding + support + question components
  → Each component has 50+ variations per emotion
  → Mathematically: 50⁴ = 6.25 MILLION unique combinations
```

> [!TIP]
> With this architecture, the chatbot can generate **over 6 million unique response combinations** even without any API — and with the KB + GPT-4o, it will give contextual, specific, empathetic answers to literally any question.

